Dependencies:
 - python-twitter with Search API support (newer than January 9, 2010)

Usage:
./twittertail.py <query> [--delay <seconds>]

To quit, just press CTRL-C at command prompt

Example:
$> ./twittertail.py twitter
aguy (Fri, 02 Apr 2010 23:57:17 +0000)
> TwitterTail is a very nice app
anotherguy (Fri, 02 Apr 2010 23:57:18 +0000, 98)
> @aguy you're right !
[... and so on ...]
